76561198072760255,Recommended,269730,11845296,"Posted: 24 August, 2014",all,Zero74,"Best Golfing game ever.....Since my review of over 2 years ago, the improvements to this game have been many. Along with the fixing of map and image glitches, the addition of the handicap system for match-making makes your online experience much fairer. The official courses range from easy (which can be fun to post pro scores!) to very difficult courses where wind, ground slope, green elevation, pace of greens and contours of greens make club selection of the utmost importance. The type of shot selected i.e. flop, chip etc. also becomes important when needing to keep your ball below the wind or to deal with  fast paced greens. I have been playing golf simulation games for over 30 years and still believe this to be the best golfing game ever! (Tiger Woods was arcady.... this is as close to a round of golf that i've found)An understanding of Golf IRL is beneficial, however learning the mechanics of this game can be enjoyable on its own.Well done to the Devs for creating and improving this game."
